Jim Doughan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jim_Doughan 0 James Francis Doughan (born August 2, 1959) is an American actor, writer, and teacher. He is perhaps best known for his roles as Detective Doyle in The Mask (1994) and Detective Allen as well as the voice of Lucky the cat in Stuart Little (1999). He is currently a performing arts teacher at Harvard-Westlake School in Los Angeles, California. James_Francis_Doughan ( born August_2_,_1959 ) is an_American_actor , writer , and teacher .
